        "subject": "LU-4053 mdt: return -ENOENT in mdt_intent_layout()",
        "message": "LU-4053 mdt: return -ENOENT in mdt_intent_layout()\n\nmdt_intent_layout should return -ENOENT for non-existing object,\notherwise, layout lock could be acquired on client for an unlinked\nobject, and that result in the inode cache for the unlinked object\ncan't be purged.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie77148932f9d59a034589d2b3a41b15722c1c3e2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
